snippet.title: Super Mario Continuance - SAGE 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Sorry- this one was made with no audio in order to make it fit into the SAGE '23 trailer... What's that? You haven't watched the whole trailer? Well what are you waiting for?! Super Mario Continuance Chapters 1&2 is only one of the many amazing games coming to Sonic Amateur Games Expo 2023, starting September 1st!: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rov4-sQuStU&t=1293s

SAGE Website: https://sagexpo.org/

Play the original MTMB games: https://ari-games.com/

Learn more about Super Mario: https://www.nintendo.com/

This game has blood and gore, as such, this trailer is !NOT FOR KIDS!
